  <div class="flex flex-wrap ">
    <div class="relative grow max-w-full flex-1 px-4">
      <h1 class="page-title">
        Missing Content
      </h1>
      <p>The page you seek may not exist. Or it may have existed in the past. Since the 1990s, DCMI has migrated its Web content between several platforms, most recently in 2018-2019, when HTML Web pages were converted into Markdown for processing into a website using <a href="https://gohugo.io/">Hugo</a>, a static site generator. The DCMI Wiki, <a href="/legacy/wikis/">http://wiki.dublincore.org/</a>, was taken down and its contents were moved into a <a href="https://github.com/dcmi/repository/">archival repository</a>.  Obsolete administrative materials were moved offline. Materials related to the activity of the <a href="/groups/usage-board/">DCMI Usage Board</a> were moved off the main website and consolidated in a Github repository, <a href="https://github.com/dcmi/usage/">usage</a>. In the course of restructuring, links were broken, though we have tried hard to mitigate their impact with aliases and redirects. If you need help finding something specific, please contact us by using the green 'Website Feedback' button above.</p>

    </div>
  </div>

